{
  "stem": "17374.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 323.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And-- oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Before this list was drawn, before this one they-- they shoot that [GERMAN] and his wife.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Monek ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Ferber, ?] I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And-- and a few others who were the higher policemen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They shoot them, and they put them down lying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And we all have to march and looked at them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But if somebody turned the head, they will shoot this person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "We don't-- we were not allowed not to look.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We have to look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "We just have to look at that dead body lying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And was-- it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And that was all Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And-- and then, I remember how they take children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "They take children from their mother's arms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And from that there was like a kindergarten or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "God knows how.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I don't know what-- the children was separately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on-- on the big buggy or was it by horse?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember the children were screaming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The mother was holding and screaming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And music was playing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know if my husband was playing or some record.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was music playing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the scream of this children and the mothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- oh, that was-- that was awful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm maybe mixing up things, but that was-- that was Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then I find out that I have to go somewhere when my husband was going to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I heard about Schindler.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw him in a beginning of the Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to march to work somewhere outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Outside.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was wire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it wasn't an electric wire in the ghetto-- in the Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just-- wire-- how you call it with this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I can go and see him through the wire.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
